WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:34.960 --> 01:37.644
=Episode 9=

01:40.336 --> 01:41.136
My lord,

01:41.936 --> 01:44.496
what were you doing
at Xu Wanzhou's courtyard?

01:45.056 --> 01:45.856
I...

01:47.657 --> 01:49.257
I heard the sound of guqin.

01:52.017 --> 01:53.657
And I saw her memorial tablet.

01:54.177 --> 01:54.977
My lord,

01:55.617 --> 01:57.177
you're talking nonsense.

01:57.657 --> 01:59.907
She was fine when she left the capital
eight years ago.

01:59.907 --> 02:01.584
How come there is
a memorial tablet of her?

02:02.657 --> 02:05.136
I... I really saw Wanzhou's
memorial tablet.

02:05.136 --> 02:07.017
Servants carried you back.

02:07.336 --> 02:10.217
That yard has been deserted for years.
There was nothing there.

02:10.377 --> 02:11.176
Really?

02:11.296 --> 02:12.097
Of course.

02:14.217 --> 02:16.257
Bring some calming tea and hot water.

02:23.257 --> 02:24.057
Your Highness,

02:28.817 --> 02:30.016
are you going to the office?

02:31.777 --> 02:33.136
Let me tidy up your clothes.

02:37.136 --> 02:38.136
Why are they wrinkled?

02:38.736 --> 02:41.217
It's my fault. I forgot
to iron His Highness's clothes.

02:41.616 --> 02:43.377
It's fine. Time's up.

02:43.537 --> 02:44.497
We have to go.

02:44.817 --> 02:47.416
I know a quick fix. It won't take long.

02:59.097 --> 03:01.777
Don't worry. I won't burn you.

03:10.537 --> 03:12.817
Southern embroiderers
all use this as a quick fix.

03:13.136 --> 03:14.777
It works better than a charcoal iron.

03:44.416 --> 03:45.377
There, done.

03:48.817 --> 03:50.977
Will Your Highness
be home for dinner today?

03:51.537 --> 03:52.377
Not necessarily.

03:53.416 --> 03:54.537
You'll come back late?

03:56.257 --> 03:57.296
Things are busy.

04:01.296 --> 04:02.337
Do you need something?

04:03.937 --> 04:05.817
I invited Senior Wei Zhuang over today.

04:07.896 --> 04:10.296
Could you come back
and join us for dinner?

04:18.697 --> 04:21.376
Your Highness, if we don't leave now,
we will be late.

04:23.256 --> 04:24.056
I'll try.

04:25.697 --> 04:26.777
Then I'll wait for you.

04:34.256 --> 04:35.176
Let's go prepare.

04:41.008 --> 04:43.440
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

04:44.577 --> 04:46.416
This prefect is newly appointed,

04:46.856 --> 04:50.736
and he brought someone
just out of jail as our colleague.

04:50.736 --> 04:53.697
I increasingly fail to understand
what our new prefect is thinking.

04:54.416 --> 04:58.457
Deputy Prefect, as the saying goes,
a new broom sweeps clean.

04:58.616 --> 05:02.496
By my reckoning, the new prefect
hasn't finished 'sweeping' yet.

05:11.657 --> 05:14.097
I'm Gu Zheng, the new scribe.

05:39.056 --> 05:40.616
Look at how full of himself he is!

05:53.137 --> 05:53.936
Your Highness,

05:55.176 --> 05:57.897
Jingzhao Prefecture affairs are complex,
and its case files numerous.

05:58.256 --> 06:00.337
Sorting them out won't be done in a day.

06:01.217 --> 06:02.657
Please don't overexert yourself.

06:03.736 --> 06:05.376
Given the way Zheng Zuoshi operates,

06:06.296 --> 06:07.657
likely earlier Gongshu Yang

06:07.657 --> 06:09.256
turned a blind eye to problems.

06:10.537 --> 06:11.936
This prefecture's issues run deep.

06:12.616 --> 06:15.256
If we don't address them in time,
they could become trickier.

06:17.017 --> 06:17.936
How is Gu Zheng doing?

06:19.416 --> 06:21.097
Scribe Fu is worth five of them.

06:21.176 --> 06:23.816
Just this morning,
all the clerks have found out

06:23.897 --> 06:26.457
that if you want things done,
you must go to Scribe Gu.

06:27.416 --> 06:28.416
Don't worry.

06:33.736 --> 06:37.337
Today the official kitchen prepared
Milk-Brewed Fish and Sweet Dew Soup.

06:37.616 --> 06:40.416
All the section heads and clerks
have gone to eat.

06:41.097 --> 06:42.056
Then let's go too.

06:44.977 --> 06:45.616
More, please.

06:51.736 --> 06:54.017
The fish is exceptionally fresh today.

06:55.056 --> 06:55.616
- Indeed.
- Not bad.

06:57.936 --> 07:00.537
Why are Deputy Prefect Zheng
and Revenue Clerk Li not here?

07:03.256 --> 07:05.376
And the atmosphere today feels off.

07:09.816 --> 07:13.936
Well, Scribe Gu is way too efficient.

07:16.176 --> 07:21.616
What do you suppose
the new prefect is actually planning?

07:23.416 --> 07:26.856
He wouldn't be considering
dismissing us all, would he?

07:28.056 --> 07:32.296
Why worry so much?
Just focus on doing your own job well.

07:34.296 --> 07:35.657
- Greetings, Prefect!
- Greetings, Prefect!

07:36.176 --> 07:37.577
- Greetings, Prefect!
- Greetings, Prefect!

07:38.256 --> 07:39.632
Greetings, Prefect.

07:39.664 --> 07:40.996
- Greetings, Prefect!
- Greetings, Prefect!

07:41.816 --> 07:43.296
Everyone, just carry on as normal.

07:43.816 --> 07:45.137
I've only recently taken charge.

07:45.616 --> 07:48.056
I should have more informal
interactions with you.

07:48.856 --> 07:50.056
Please don't feel constrained.

07:50.816 --> 07:51.977
- Yes.
- Yes.

07:58.217 --> 07:59.097
Getting used to it?

07:59.816 --> 08:02.416
Work is work regardless of location.
Nothing to get used to.

08:03.616 --> 08:04.616
Why aren't you sitting?

08:13.616 --> 08:15.537
Prefect, I am newly married.

08:15.537 --> 08:17.736
Today, my wife specially
prepared grilled lamb.

08:17.736 --> 08:20.056
If you don't disdain it,
please try some.

08:25.256 --> 08:26.616
Not to boast,

08:26.897 --> 08:28.856
but my wife's cooking is quite decent.

08:30.616 --> 08:31.616
Scribe Gu, try some too.

08:31.777 --> 08:33.536
See how it compares to the food here.

08:34.697 --> 08:36.417
Thank you, Judicial Clerk Zhang.

08:41.297 --> 08:42.136
Take your time.

08:42.136 --> 08:42.896
Thank you.

08:49.256 --> 08:50.057
Your Highness.

08:53.616 --> 08:55.457
Could you come back
and join us for dinner?

08:56.144 --> 08:59.616
♪Fortunately, the wounds
the world gave me♪

08:59.616 --> 09:00.457
Jin.

09:03.097 --> 09:05.417
Tell my wife that I will
return home for dinner.

09:07.312 --> 09:10.376
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

09:10.376 --> 09:11.896
Qi sinks to the Yongquan points.

09:13.136 --> 09:15.697
Strength permeates the Laogong points.

09:17.697 --> 09:18.896
Where are the Laogong points?

09:18.896 --> 09:19.616
Palm centers.

09:19.616 --> 09:20.136
I see.

09:20.136 --> 09:21.097
Step out wider.

09:26.457 --> 09:28.656
You're about to poke holes
in these bamboo strips.

09:30.177 --> 09:32.656
Must have drunk too much last night.
I can't straighten up.

09:33.776 --> 09:34.697
Your Highness.

09:35.417 --> 09:36.217
Wei Zhuang.

09:38.672 --> 09:41.697
♪In the vast world,
longing only for some moonlight♪

09:41.697 --> 09:43.937
This bamboo hoop got bent.

09:44.297 --> 09:46.136
The whole hoop leans right.

09:46.656 --> 09:49.496
The following ones
will tilt and spin wildly.

09:49.496 --> 09:51.217
Use fire to heat and bend it.

09:52.144 --> 09:57.663
♪Shimmering years
are filled with poetic chapters♪

09:57.977 --> 10:00.136
When did you learn kite-making,
Wei Zhuang?

10:00.656 --> 10:02.697
Ji could make kites
when she was very young.

10:02.697 --> 10:03.656
I learned it from her.

10:03.656 --> 10:05.936
♪To share it with you♪

10:07.337 --> 10:08.656
Why make a kite?

10:09.457 --> 10:12.097
It's a homework assignment
left by a tutor for Wuyou.

10:12.136 --> 10:13.016
We're helping him.

10:16.977 --> 10:19.977
This thing's so slow.
Can it even hit anyone?

10:20.977 --> 10:22.616
This is the Eight-Desolation Fist.

10:23.136 --> 10:25.977
An old Daoist master taught it to me.

10:26.776 --> 10:28.536
It strengthens the body

10:29.536 --> 10:32.496
and enables scaling walls.

10:33.177 --> 10:34.977
But I heard from the servants

10:35.097 --> 10:39.297
that you ran here
because you're scared of losing fights.

10:39.297 --> 10:41.856
I told you, this fist art
strengthens the body.

10:42.016 --> 10:45.057
For actual fighting, use this.

10:45.496 --> 10:46.297
You're lying!

10:46.516 --> 10:47.016
I'm lying?

10:47.016 --> 10:48.256
Wuyou, look.

10:48.977 --> 10:51.057
- A big centipede.
- Thank you, Aunt!

10:52.337 --> 10:53.697
The centipede is ready!

10:54.057 --> 10:54.776
Careful.

10:54.977 --> 10:55.697
A big centipede!

10:55.697 --> 10:57.457
Spin. Spin it around.

10:57.457 --> 10:58.177
Flying centipede!

10:58.177 --> 10:59.256
- Great!
- Centipede!

11:00.057 --> 11:00.616
Centipede!

11:01.417 --> 11:02.656
Run faster.

11:03.057 --> 11:04.376
Flying centipede!

11:06.224 --> 11:10.793
♪Lost with you in these fleeting years♪

11:10.793 --> 11:13.296
♪The world's chaos♪

11:13.296 --> 11:17.744
♪Becomes irrelevant♪

11:20.905 --> 11:24.048
♪No matter how small a place♪

11:24.369 --> 11:26.656
♪By each other's faint light♪

11:26.656 --> 11:29.256
Uncle, look! The centipede's flying!

11:29.896 --> 11:31.577
The centipede's flying!

11:34.448 --> 11:36.784
♪With your lingering fragrance♪

11:36.784 --> 11:38.736
♪Toward days we have♪

11:38.736 --> 11:39.776
Your Highness is back.

11:39.776 --> 11:43.088
♪A river of longing reflects in my gaze♪

11:43.088 --> 11:45.392
♪Let all worries rest deep inside♪

11:46.057 --> 11:47.817
I once promised Tao and Xing

11:48.297 --> 11:50.977
that if my stones bloomed,
I'd hold a banquet.

11:51.376 --> 11:54.057
One has really bloomed,
which is a good omen.

11:54.536 --> 11:56.217
So, I wanted us to get together.

11:57.177 --> 11:59.057
All seated are family
of Prince Ding's Mansion.

11:59.577 --> 12:00.817
Today, we rejoice together.

12:01.136 --> 12:02.032
My toast to you all!

12:04.616 --> 12:06.256
- Thank you, Your Highness.
- Thank you, Your Highness.

12:11.256 --> 12:12.297
Let's eat.

12:14.376 --> 12:14.977
Eat.

12:17.177 --> 12:20.256
You prepared this lavish feast yourself?

12:20.977 --> 12:24.016
Not me, the mansion's kitchen staff did.

12:28.896 --> 12:32.177
Ms. Wen, I've long been duly honored.

12:32.297 --> 12:34.577
Meeting confirms your jade-like warmth

12:34.656 --> 12:35.896
and extraordinary presence.

12:37.016 --> 12:39.417
How could you possibly know of me?

12:40.177 --> 12:43.817
Rather, I've often heard you possess
exceptional talent in Daoist arts.

12:44.937 --> 12:48.856
Talent? Hardly.
I just grasp innate principles.

12:49.417 --> 12:51.776
The Dao is quite simple.

12:52.016 --> 12:53.536
Like this stick of sandalwood incense.

12:53.736 --> 12:55.417
Yesterday's ashes have fallen.

12:55.417 --> 12:58.136
Today's seal script lingers.

12:58.297 --> 13:00.697
And tomorrow's wind source is unknown.

13:01.337 --> 13:02.496
All with cause and effect.

13:03.577 --> 13:04.896
Yesterday's fish wasn't fresh,

13:05.217 --> 13:06.616
and no fish for the day after.

13:07.016 --> 13:09.057
Uncle Wenshen, enjoy this fish now.

13:09.297 --> 13:10.016
Be good.

13:10.057 --> 13:11.057
Eat properly.

13:11.760 --> 13:13.656
Keep chatting,
and you return to Longevity Shop

13:13.656 --> 13:15.057
to talk with that general.

13:15.817 --> 13:17.616
Ms. Wen, eat fish.

13:18.496 --> 13:20.136
Your Highness may not know.

13:20.337 --> 13:22.896
Life on the mountain
truly lacked clothes and food.

13:22.937 --> 13:26.417
Post-sealing, there were
no markets to buy from.

13:26.856 --> 13:29.016
All supplies had to be self-sufficient.

13:30.097 --> 13:32.776
Life was extremely hard.

13:33.817 --> 13:36.656
These years,
Her Highness truly suffered.

13:39.297 --> 13:41.217
Luckily, she found Your Highness.

13:42.376 --> 13:43.776
With hearts united as a couple,

13:44.457 --> 13:46.616
the days ahead are bound to improve.

13:48.817 --> 13:49.656
I appreciate it.

13:57.577 --> 13:58.077
By the way,

13:58.817 --> 14:01.457
you really managed
to make the stone bloom?

14:02.057 --> 14:02.817
Want to see it?

14:02.817 --> 14:03.376
Of course.

14:03.736 --> 14:04.536
It's right there.

14:10.256 --> 14:12.217
Look, this little sprout
is growing so well.

14:13.376 --> 14:14.177
Good.

14:15.697 --> 14:17.577
Well, your foot

14:18.376 --> 14:20.656
seemed a bit unsteady, right?

14:20.896 --> 14:21.417
It was.

14:21.937 --> 14:23.217
Her Highness fixed it for me.

14:23.417 --> 14:26.337
It's much better now. Look.

14:26.856 --> 14:28.577
Li is truly skilled.

14:28.616 --> 14:30.736
Learned many fine skills
on the mountain.

14:31.656 --> 14:33.177
His Highness is truly fortunate.

14:51.937 --> 14:52.697
Your Highness!

15:02.057 --> 15:03.057
Where's Jin?

15:03.817 --> 15:05.376
He's gone to make sobering soup.

15:07.457 --> 15:10.136
I'll fetch some water.
You should wash your face.

15:26.937 --> 15:28.057
Then do it yourself.

15:43.057 --> 15:43.856
Your Highness,

15:45.577 --> 15:46.896
let me treat your legs.

15:49.297 --> 15:51.097
Today you saw Wei Zhuang too.

15:51.977 --> 15:54.736
He had a limp before,
and I treated him and fixed it.

15:55.097 --> 15:56.536
With years on Lishan Mountain,

15:56.896 --> 15:59.136
I studied medicine under Master Helai.

15:59.937 --> 16:02.416
I learned herb identification,
acupuncture, and everything.

16:02.697 --> 16:05.136
My main research
was on how to treat leg ailments.

16:07.496 --> 16:10.496
Actually, your legs do have sensation.

16:11.977 --> 16:14.817
You can kneel-sit and flex them.

16:15.256 --> 16:16.736
They can react instinctively.

16:17.457 --> 16:18.776
I can cure them.

16:19.536 --> 16:22.697
I know you've sought treatment
many times before,

16:23.297 --> 16:26.536
seen many physicians,
and been through a lot.

16:28.536 --> 16:31.896
But could you try one more time for me?

16:37.656 --> 16:38.937
Why are you staring at me?

16:54.776 --> 17:00.177
I recall the Lishan Academy wrote
a book called Healing the World.

17:01.057 --> 17:02.016
It says within,

17:02.856 --> 17:04.177
"Hold a mirror to straighten up;"

17:05.897 --> 17:08.377
"measure grain to sustain nourishment."

17:09.177 --> 17:10.377
"Cultivate virtue within;"

17:10.697 --> 17:11.937
"measure kindness without."

17:12.217 --> 17:13.617
"Thus one may live a lifetime."

17:16.377 --> 17:17.016
Ye Li,

17:18.697 --> 17:19.816
after leaving the mountain,

17:20.697 --> 17:22.016
you've aided Wei Zhuang,

17:22.457 --> 17:23.897
your uncle Wenshen,

17:24.256 --> 17:25.417
Wuyou,

17:25.776 --> 17:26.897
and my sister-in-law.

17:28.576 --> 17:30.056
Now it's time to help me?

17:33.697 --> 17:35.096
Why do you think

17:36.377 --> 17:37.857
that you can help me?

17:40.336 --> 17:41.137
Or rather,

17:42.336 --> 17:46.016
how do you think you're better
than those Imperial Physicians

17:47.697 --> 17:50.217
and those renowned physicians I've seen?

18:13.937 --> 18:15.016
In this world,

18:18.496 --> 18:20.056
those overflowing with kindness

18:20.937 --> 18:22.296
seldom meet good ends.

18:33.657 --> 18:35.657
If you don't want
to stay married to a cripple,

18:36.776 --> 18:38.016
you may leave anytime.

18:42.192 --> 18:45.296
(Tuisi Pavilion)

18:58.776 --> 18:59.576
(Wait.)

19:03.897 --> 19:05.536
Prince Ding's household once helped me.

19:05.736 --> 19:08.137
I wish to offer General Mo
a last drink before he's executed.

19:14.977 --> 19:15.776
Let her through.

19:28.137 --> 19:29.617
I am Xu Wanzhou's daughter.

19:30.377 --> 19:31.857
She had a message for me to pass on.

19:32.657 --> 19:33.977
She said she's sorry to you.

19:34.056 --> 19:35.177
Why didn't she come herself?

19:38.897 --> 19:39.816
She couldn't come.

19:41.977 --> 19:44.576
My mother said
the Lishan Academy owes you a debt.

19:45.256 --> 19:46.736
We'll try to make amends.

19:47.816 --> 19:49.336
Is there any other wish you have?

19:49.776 --> 19:50.576
My brother...

19:54.496 --> 19:55.377
They said

19:57.096 --> 19:59.336
he broke both legs at Suixue Pass.

19:59.937 --> 20:01.056
I am going to die.

20:02.457 --> 20:03.937
But you must save him.

20:05.857 --> 20:07.736
Alright, I promise you.

20:18.496 --> 20:19.256
Who's it?

20:19.816 --> 20:21.937
I'm passing by.
Sun's hot, and I'm thirsty.

20:22.417 --> 20:24.657
I'd like to beg the old master
for a last drink.

20:26.056 --> 20:27.617
A young lady?

20:28.016 --> 20:30.056
Whose life do you want to buy?

20:31.617 --> 20:32.937
I don't do bloody business.

20:33.217 --> 20:36.496
(Zheng Qin, Leader of Chiwu Gang)
Please abduct someone for me. Alive.

20:36.496 --> 20:37.857
Don't harm a hair on them.

20:38.096 --> 20:39.496
But the target's not low-ranking.

20:39.657 --> 20:40.736
You lot might not dare.

20:40.857 --> 20:42.857
Now that's an insult.

20:43.137 --> 20:45.536
I don't care
about so-called noble blood.

20:46.336 --> 20:48.296
Only silver and gold.

20:51.016 --> 20:52.457
About when exactly to move,

20:52.736 --> 20:53.697
wait for my signal.

21:00.336 --> 21:02.776
Revenue Clerk Li,
the prefect requests you.

21:06.096 --> 21:08.296
The Prefect calls. Go.

21:09.296 --> 21:09.796
Yes.

21:25.016 --> 21:27.137
You've dared bring
all those filthy schemes

21:27.657 --> 21:29.736
stewing inside you
to the Jingzhao Prefecture?

21:30.857 --> 21:33.736
I haven't! I truly don't know!

21:33.857 --> 21:34.897
You don't know?

21:35.937 --> 21:37.457
Well, I know perfectly well.

21:41.056 --> 21:41.857
Look!

21:43.536 --> 21:46.457
Are the figures
in this account book correct?

21:49.296 --> 21:50.657
Seizing farmland from commoners,

21:51.377 --> 21:52.776
faking accounts for profit,

21:53.256 --> 21:54.776
favoritism, and bending the law.

21:56.016 --> 22:00.177
Li Yufeng, you've been Revenue Clerk
for the Jingzhao Prefecture for years.

22:00.377 --> 22:02.096
Your monthly stipend is significant.

22:02.377 --> 22:03.937
Nor is your year-end payment low.

22:04.897 --> 22:06.417
You're fed by the people's taxes.

22:06.776 --> 22:08.937
Yet you have the gall
to bleed the people dry.

22:09.977 --> 22:11.496
A shame upon the Jingzhao Prefecture!

22:16.496 --> 22:18.217
Li Yufeng, you're corrupt and lawless.

22:18.897 --> 22:23.096
I hereby dismiss you
from your position forthwith.

22:23.977 --> 22:26.857
All proceeds from your embezzlement
will be sealed.

22:27.296 --> 22:28.417
You await judgment.

22:29.177 --> 22:32.256
Also, draft a report
for the Ministry of Personnel fast.

22:32.256 --> 22:37.096
Scribe Gu Zheng will temporarily
fill the position of Revenue Clerk here.

22:39.897 --> 22:41.336
As you command.

22:42.177 --> 22:43.536
Hold on!

22:44.336 --> 22:45.576
Even if I have faults,

22:45.977 --> 22:48.857
it shouldn't lead
to such a hasty dismissal.

22:49.217 --> 22:50.016
Right.

22:52.624 --> 22:54.016
By Chu Code with Commentary,

22:54.016 --> 22:58.217
the Imperial Court of Judicial Review
and the Censorate must vet all removals.

22:59.096 --> 23:02.177
Prefect Mo, such a hasty dismissal
probably violates protocol.

23:02.617 --> 23:05.177
Since I've taken the post
of Jingzhao Prefect,

23:06.016 --> 23:07.617
I bear this responsibility.

23:08.417 --> 23:11.937
Here, my words are the rule.

23:12.977 --> 23:15.816
If you disagree,
feel free to petition the court.

23:17.137 --> 23:17.857
Take him away.

23:17.857 --> 23:20.256
Wait! Your Highness! Your Highness!

23:21.457 --> 23:23.457
Master Li, please.

23:24.697 --> 23:26.617
Deputy Prefect, help! Help!

23:26.617 --> 23:27.496
(The Office)

23:27.496 --> 23:28.697
Now, listen well, all of you.

23:36.496 --> 23:39.417
Your little schemes
are perfectly clear to me.

23:40.417 --> 23:42.137
Best to put those ideas away now.

23:42.417 --> 23:46.736
If each of you fulfills
your duties with diligence,

23:47.096 --> 23:48.977
we'll naturally coexist peacefully.

23:50.617 --> 23:55.697
But should any slack off
and neglect duties,

23:57.177 --> 24:00.336
I can readily seek better replacements.

24:03.417 --> 24:07.016
As for collusion and corruption,

24:08.177 --> 24:09.857
that will not be tolerated.

24:10.697 --> 24:11.496
- Yes.
- Yes.

24:13.897 --> 24:14.736
Sesame cakes!

24:16.697 --> 24:18.076
Here you are.

24:18.417 --> 24:18.937
Alright.

24:19.677 --> 24:20.816
Here you go. Take care.

24:20.816 --> 24:21.576
I'll have the same.

24:21.576 --> 24:22.336
Alright.

24:53.136 --> 24:53.872
(Red Fox)

24:54.417 --> 24:57.016
Red Fox, why are you following me?

24:57.056 --> 24:59.417
Master commands me to bring you back.

25:00.217 --> 25:01.336
Bring me back?

25:01.776 --> 25:03.256
Do you have what it takes?

25:32.657 --> 25:35.336
Back on the training field,
the head instructor used to say,

25:35.937 --> 25:39.776
"If killers dare not draw their blades,
they're destined to fail."

25:40.736 --> 25:41.816
Don't you remember?

25:45.937 --> 25:47.137
Go back and tell Han Mingyue

25:47.137 --> 25:49.857
that I'll repay all he spent
raising me and saving my life.

25:51.536 --> 25:52.816
But I am not his brother.

26:37.417 --> 26:38.177
What's wrong?

26:40.417 --> 26:41.377
Her Highness is here.

26:41.496 --> 26:43.536
She didn't want to disturb you.

27:07.536 --> 27:08.937
Greetings, Your Highness.

27:10.296 --> 27:13.937
I am Wei Chengli, Personnel Clerk
for Jingzhao Prefecture.

27:15.137 --> 27:17.576
The weather is quite hot.

27:17.576 --> 27:20.897
Perhaps Your Highness would like
to step inside for some tea?

27:21.217 --> 27:24.137
I just brewed a pot
of fine Lushan Yunwu tea.

27:24.137 --> 27:27.657
You can enjoy the tea
while waiting for the prefect.

27:28.457 --> 27:29.576
That won't be necessary.

27:29.977 --> 27:32.217
I'll just sun myself here.

27:33.857 --> 27:35.937
Does Your Highness like grasshoppers?

27:35.937 --> 27:39.717
Perfect. I have at home a painting
by Master Wu,

27:39.717 --> 27:42.736
'Moonlit Night Chirping.'

27:42.897 --> 27:46.736
The grasshoppers in it are depicted
with stunning realism.

27:47.137 --> 27:47.937
Later...

27:48.736 --> 27:49.236
No.

27:54.816 --> 27:56.816
Your Highness, you're on break?

27:57.336 --> 27:58.256
Came to see you.

27:58.897 --> 28:02.617
I suddenly recall some minor matters
in my office that need attending to.

28:03.137 --> 28:03.937
I take my leave.

28:07.137 --> 28:07.977
Need something?

28:08.617 --> 28:10.217
Would you come with me to offer incense?

28:10.536 --> 28:12.697
It's the Zhengyi Temple
outside the city. Very close.

28:13.016 --> 28:15.016
We can go today and return tomorrow.

28:15.440 --> 28:16.776
Have you asked our sister-in-law?

28:17.016 --> 28:18.377
I already asked her.

28:18.617 --> 28:21.457
She said her nephew was sick
and she had to visit.

28:22.056 --> 28:24.417
I have no one else, so I came to you.

28:26.736 --> 28:28.137
My schedule is packed today.

28:28.536 --> 28:30.417
I might be working very late.

28:30.576 --> 28:31.377
That's fine.

28:32.217 --> 28:35.496
The weather is nice today,
and the views here are pleasant.

28:35.816 --> 28:36.897
I'll just sit here

28:36.977 --> 28:38.937
to wait for you
while enjoying the views.

28:40.137 --> 28:41.056
Go ahead and work.

28:55.440 --> 28:59.248
(Jingzhao Prefecture)

29:19.736 --> 29:20.296
Jin.

29:22.417 --> 29:24.087
Take all these over to Gu Zheng.

29:24.087 --> 29:25.857
Tell him to carefully review them

29:26.296 --> 29:28.417
and reply to me
before Shen hour tomorrow.

29:28.977 --> 29:29.477
Yes.

29:34.937 --> 29:35.897
It's so quiet outside.

29:39.336 --> 29:40.016
Your Highness,

29:40.977 --> 29:42.977
your duty shift ended long ago.

29:43.177 --> 29:44.617
Why aren't you heading home?

29:47.056 --> 29:47.816
And my wife?

29:49.177 --> 29:49.977
She left.

29:50.657 --> 29:51.457
She returned home?

29:54.096 --> 29:55.496
It was already very late.

29:55.496 --> 29:57.576
As for offering incense,
any day will do.

30:00.816 --> 30:01.697
You deliver these.

30:03.977 --> 30:04.477
Yes.

30:11.696 --> 30:13.968
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

30:31.336 --> 30:34.377
Just as I thought, Her Highness
must be asleep this late.

30:34.457 --> 30:36.177
She couldn't eat
the honey cakes you bought.

30:49.137 --> 30:50.137
They're yours.

30:53.256 --> 30:54.657
Thank Her Highness.

31:04.056 --> 31:04.776
Your Highness.

31:06.217 --> 31:07.897
Your Highness,
let's go chase butterflies.

31:09.617 --> 31:10.377
Uninteresting.

31:11.977 --> 31:14.217
I heard Jinxiu Shop
has new Yunjin brocade.

31:14.336 --> 31:16.776
How about I go with you
to pick out some new robes?

31:18.336 --> 31:19.217
Not interested.

31:25.776 --> 31:26.512
Your Highness!

31:28.576 --> 31:30.256
Jinxiu Shop has new Yunjin brocade.

31:30.617 --> 31:32.617
Could I accompany you
to have some new robes made?

31:32.937 --> 31:35.576
Go yourself. I have matters these days.

31:35.897 --> 31:36.697
I will be very busy.

31:37.496 --> 31:38.296
Your Highness.

31:42.256 --> 31:45.256
Your Highness, should we still go?

31:46.697 --> 31:47.697
Of course we're not!

32:03.336 --> 32:05.736
Shall I wake her for you?

32:12.657 --> 32:13.457
Your Highness?

32:14.857 --> 32:15.657
Your Highness?

32:16.857 --> 32:19.096
Wake up. His Highness
brought you tasty food.

32:20.496 --> 32:21.296
Your Highness?

32:22.937 --> 32:25.296
If you keep sleeping,
I'll eat the honey cakes.

32:26.697 --> 32:28.897
Your Highness, is Her Highness not here?

32:46.576 --> 32:48.897
Xiuyao, you're back.
What are you doing here?

32:48.897 --> 32:49.576
Sister-in-law.

32:51.016 --> 32:54.016
I bought some honey cakes
and wanted to ask if Li would like any.

32:54.576 --> 32:57.177
Li went to Zhengyi Temple.
She isn't back yet.

32:57.536 --> 32:58.697
To Zhengyi Temple?

33:00.657 --> 33:01.617
When did she leave?

33:02.217 --> 33:05.137
She left three or four days ago.
Didn't she tell you?

33:16.137 --> 33:17.496
Boundless benevolence.

33:22.736 --> 33:23.657
Thank you.

33:24.528 --> 33:26.896
(Zhengyi Temple)

33:31.016 --> 33:32.016
That's wrong.

33:32.784 --> 33:35.697
Why would the Divine Maiden be smiling?

33:36.177 --> 33:38.296
Even the souls in hell
are bound by reincarnation.

33:39.016 --> 33:40.336
The Divine Maiden is merciful.

33:40.977 --> 33:42.657
Upon seeing them suffer endlessly,

33:43.256 --> 33:44.736
how could she not feel grieved?

33:44.937 --> 33:48.056
In my view, the Divine Maiden
should look sorrowful.

33:49.137 --> 33:50.897
Yunsong, do not be hasty.

33:52.056 --> 33:55.536
These souls in hell
committed numerous evils in life.

33:55.816 --> 33:58.776
Their suffering
is the karmic retribution they bear,

33:59.137 --> 34:00.377
the fruit of their own deeds.

34:01.576 --> 34:05.457
Only by repaying their karmic debts
and severing past causes

34:05.657 --> 34:07.657
can they attain enlightenment.

34:08.457 --> 34:10.377
The Divine Maiden
has grasped the supreme Dao,

34:10.616 --> 34:12.857
understanding the world's truths.

34:13.216 --> 34:16.817
Seeing sinful souls have due retribution
and gain hope for rebirth

34:17.016 --> 34:20.737
naturally comforts her heart,
knowing beings are liberated.

34:20.857 --> 34:22.536
Hence, she smiles joyfully.

34:22.536 --> 34:23.616
Utter nonsense!

34:23.857 --> 34:26.937
What kind of Divine Maiden smiles
while watching living beings suffer?

34:27.056 --> 34:29.216
Master Du, you are mistaken.

34:29.417 --> 34:30.457
What would you know?

34:30.457 --> 34:32.937
She understands
the mysteries of heaven's cycle

34:33.257 --> 34:34.576
and knows karma's principle

34:34.608 --> 34:35.777
and retribution's certainty,

34:35.777 --> 34:37.216
so she transcends the world.

34:39.656 --> 34:40.616
What is she doing?

34:41.096 --> 34:42.737
You... stop that!

34:42.897 --> 34:44.857
Come down from there!

34:46.176 --> 34:47.337
Only those who do not contend

34:48.457 --> 34:50.176
can truly transcend the world.

34:58.176 --> 34:58.977
Your Highness.

35:37.056 --> 35:38.377
She seems to smile, yet not.

35:39.616 --> 35:40.857
She seems to weep, yet not.

35:42.536 --> 35:44.857
Both compassionate and solemn.

35:46.257 --> 35:47.216
Brilliant!

36:29.536 --> 36:31.056
Some people are utterly capable,

36:31.857 --> 36:33.377
daring to come up the mountain alone

36:33.977 --> 36:35.656
and not returning home for days.

36:36.737 --> 36:38.616
Do you even remember
you are a married woman?

36:39.857 --> 36:41.656
The household affairs go unattended,

36:42.176 --> 36:43.737
yet you just left as you pleased.

36:44.297 --> 36:45.096
If I had not come,

36:45.857 --> 36:47.216
how long did you plan to stay?

36:47.417 --> 36:48.656
Do you even plan on returning?

36:48.777 --> 36:49.656
Do you know I...

36:54.257 --> 36:55.056
You what?

36:57.417 --> 36:58.937
I didn't just leave as I pleased.

36:59.656 --> 37:01.056
I sent a letter to the mansion,

37:01.056 --> 37:02.768
saying I'd return
once the mural was done.

37:03.216 --> 37:04.857
I didn't come alone either.

37:05.216 --> 37:07.257
Senior Wei Zhuang accompanied me.

37:07.977 --> 37:11.056
If anything happens, he'd certainly
be able to take care of me.

37:12.297 --> 37:15.417
Besides, I'm here on important business.

37:15.656 --> 37:16.616
What important business?

37:17.417 --> 37:18.417
Painting the mural?

37:20.737 --> 37:24.216
At Shende Shop, someone offered
a high price for a painting by Yunsong.

37:24.656 --> 37:27.377
Knowing he was here, I came right away.

37:27.377 --> 37:30.817
Yunsong? The author
of Drunken Moon Chant?

37:31.136 --> 37:31.937
That's him.

37:32.576 --> 37:35.257
They say he travels year-round,
writing poetry and painting.

37:35.536 --> 37:36.817
Why is he here?

37:37.616 --> 37:40.136
About two years ago, he traveled here.

37:40.377 --> 37:41.777
He passed out drunk in the hall.

37:41.937 --> 37:43.417
That night, he had a dream.

37:44.536 --> 37:47.176
In the dream, he arrived
at a mystic realm.

37:47.777 --> 37:50.656
He saw countless ghosts
being punished, wailing in agony.

37:50.937 --> 37:52.377
It was truly a scene from hell.

37:53.056 --> 37:56.216
Then the Divine Maiden descended,
bathing them all in celestial light

37:56.457 --> 37:57.977
to ease all their misery.

37:59.857 --> 38:01.817
So it's the mural you're painting?

38:02.536 --> 38:06.136
Yes. He believes
that portraying the Divine Maiden

38:06.136 --> 38:08.056
can save people from suffering.

38:08.616 --> 38:11.616
But the work is too much.
He's been painting it for two years now.

38:12.417 --> 38:15.312
In these two years, many scholars
came specifically for him.

38:15.376 --> 38:18.377
Here, they talk poetry,
make friends, paint, and drink.

38:19.337 --> 38:22.016
When I arrived,
the work was nearly finished.

38:22.136 --> 38:24.857
It should've been done tonight
for us to leave by dawn.

38:25.536 --> 38:27.817
I didn't expect you would arrive
at this moment.

38:28.977 --> 38:29.777
As a princess con...

38:32.616 --> 38:34.257
They don't know I'm a princess consort.

38:34.616 --> 38:36.817
Here, just call me Lady Ye.

38:38.576 --> 38:42.656
Lady Ye, do you know
what Xiuyao meant to say earlier?

38:44.216 --> 38:45.016
I don't.

38:45.536 --> 38:48.576
He wanted to say that someone
was waiting for you at the mansion.

38:48.817 --> 38:52.216
That person tossed and turned
all night, unable to sleep.

38:52.257 --> 38:53.817
If the city gates hadn't been closed,

38:53.857 --> 38:56.656
they would have hitched the carriage
and rushed over immediately.

39:00.096 --> 39:00.857
Really?

39:01.656 --> 39:02.737
Ignore his nonsense.

39:04.417 --> 39:05.817
Are your things packed?

39:06.056 --> 39:09.656
If we leave now, we can still get back
before the city gates close.

39:10.777 --> 39:11.937
We can't leave tonight.

39:12.616 --> 39:13.417
Why not?

39:13.817 --> 39:15.536
I haven't got Yunsong's painting yet.

39:16.016 --> 39:19.056
He said he'd paint it tonight
and give it to me tomorrow morning.

39:20.777 --> 39:23.777
Your Highness,
could we stay one more night?

39:34.576 --> 39:35.377
Alright.

39:57.016 --> 39:58.817
Is this the only empty room available?

39:59.056 --> 40:00.576
Zhengyi Temple isn't very big.

40:00.977 --> 40:02.216
And many scholars are visiting.

40:02.737 --> 40:04.857
Others are crammed
four or five to a room.

40:05.377 --> 40:09.016
This room was specially
cleared out for me.

40:10.857 --> 40:13.937
Besides, as husband and wife,
should we really sleep apart?

40:16.857 --> 40:17.777
I'll handle it.

40:28.977 --> 40:30.176
Then let me help you change.

40:31.257 --> 40:32.216
Put it down over there.

41:19.377 --> 41:20.656
Your belt isn't fastened.

41:21.457 --> 41:22.417
Let me help you.

41:54.656 --> 41:55.457
Smells good?

41:56.897 --> 41:59.817
I washed my hair
with orchids this morning.

42:00.056 --> 42:01.096
The scent is quite fresh.

42:01.777 --> 42:03.377
If you're not rushing to leave tomorrow,

42:03.457 --> 42:06.297
I could gather some more orchids
from the back hill for your bath.

42:09.056 --> 42:12.056
No need. It's late. Let's rest.

42:13.897 --> 42:14.656
Alright.

42:31.056 --> 42:32.056
Aren't you sleeping?

42:32.457 --> 42:33.576
I'll read for a bit longer.

42:37.216 --> 42:38.257
What are you reading?

42:41.496 --> 42:42.768
Travels Across the Four Seas?

42:43.760 --> 42:46.704
(Preview)

42:47.656 --> 42:48.696
Mom,

42:49.377 --> 42:53.016
you hoped I would find
a good husband someday.

42:53.897 --> 42:55.216
I've found one.

42:55.737 --> 42:57.257
I hope, knowing from the heavens,

42:58.216 --> 42:59.457
(Tomb of Xu Wanzhou, Beloved Mother)
you can rest assured now.

43:00.496 --> 43:02.297
You're the physician's disciple?

43:03.216 --> 43:06.696
If you can't speak, could you please
find someone else to help me?

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
